object.script:
--Global Init tickrate = 60
t = 0 e = 0 old_e = 0 de = 0 old_de = 0 dde = 0
-- Tick func function onTick() --Get properties k1 = input.getNumber(3) k2 = input.getNumber(4) k3 = input.getNumber(5)
--Get current values p = input.getNumber(1) -- This is the current RPS value s = input.getNumber(2) -- This is the desired RPS value
--Update error old_e = e e = s-p
--Update delta error old_de = de de = (e - old_e)*tickrate
--Update delta delta error dde = (de - old_de)*tickrate
--Calculate delta throttle dt = k1*e + k2*de + k3*dde
--Calculate new throttle t = clamp(t + dt/tickrate, 0, 1)
--Set throttle output.setNumber(1, t)
end
function clamp(value, min, max) if value > max then return max elseif value < min then return min else return value end end

x=0 y=0 z=0 k=0 set1=0 set2=0 cH=0 per100=0 fuel=0 absCH=0 cMin = 0 minToFill = 0 cSec = 0 sector1=1 sector2=0 r=0 g=0 b=0 gen=0 s=screen i=input i.gn=i.getNumber i.gb=i.getBool s.dt=s.drawText s.sc=s.setColor s.dl=s.drawLine s.dF=s.drawRectF covt=0
function onTick() speed=i.gn(11) fluidLvl=i.gn(12) capacity=i.gn(13) sector1=i.gn(14) dist=i.gn(15) sector2=i.gn(16) gen=i.gn(20) genPress=i.gn(21) blink=i.gb(10) r=i.gn(17) g=i.gn(18) b=i.gn(19) percent=fluidLvl/capacity if dist==1 then covt=3.6 elseif dist==2 then covt=2.236936 elseif dist==3 then covt=1.943844 end if x~=601 then x=x+1 y=y+fluidLvl z=z+fluidLvl end if x==300 then set1=z/600 z=0 end if x==600 then set2=y/600 cH=math.floor((set1-set2)*720) per100=math.floor(cH/((speed*covt)/100)) fuel=math.floor(set2) absCH=math.abs(cH) reachD=math.floor((fuel/per100)*100) cMin=math.floor(math.abs((set1-set2)*12)) cSec=math.floor((math.abs((set1-set2)/5))*100)/100 minToFill=math.floor(math.abs((capacity-set2)/cMin)) ge=math.floor(gen) delta=math.floor((gen/cH)*1000) x=0 y=0 end if k ~= 1200 then k=k+1 end inputX=i.gn(3) inputY=i.gn(4) isPressed=i.gb(1) iPRa = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 0, 32, 13) output.setBool(1, iPRa) iPRa2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 14, 64, 13) output.setBool(2, iPRa2) end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() --s.sc(70, 70, 70) --if k == 1200 then -- s.drawTextBox(2, 2, 60, 5, "consumption", 0, 0) --else --if blink then -- s.drawTextBox(2, 2, 60, 5, "loading", 0, 0) -- end --end s.sc(10, 10, 10) s.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 28) s.sc(70, 70, 70)
if iPRa then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dF(0, 0, 32, 13) end if iPRa2 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dF(0, 14, 64, 13) end
s.sc(70, 70, 70)
if sector1 == 1 then s.dt(2, 1, "L/") s.dt(11, 1, "HOUR") elseif sector1 == 2 then s.dt(2, 1, "L/MIN") elseif sector1 == 3 then s.dt(2, 1, "L/SEC") end s.sc(r, g, b) if cH > 2 then if sector1 == 1 then s.dt(2, 7, cH) elseif sector1 == 2 then s.dt(2, 7, cMin) elseif sector1 == 3 then s.dt(2, 7, cSec) end else s.dt(2, 7, "--") end screen.sc(70, 70, 70) if sector2 == 1 then if covt == 3.6 then s.dt(1, 15, "L/") s.dt(9, 15, "1") s.dt(13, 15, "00km") elseif covt == 2.236936 then s.dt(1, 15, "L/") s.dt(9, 15, "1") s.dt(13, 15, "00miels") elseif covt == 1.943844 then s.dt(1, 15, "L/") s.dt(9, 15, "1") s.dt(13, 15, "00KNOTS") end s.sc(r, g, b) if speed > 5 then s.dt(2, 21, per100) else s.dt(2, 21, "--") end
elseif sector2 == 4 then s.dt(2, 15, "Effcy") s.sc(r, g, b) s.dt(2, 21, delta)
elseif sector2 == 3 then s.sc(70, 70, 70) s.dt(2, 15, "FUEL L") s.sc(r, g, b) s.dt(2, 21, fuel)
elseif sector2 == 2 then s.sc(70, 70, 70) if covt == 3.6 then s.dt(2, 15, "rng KM") elseif covt == 2.236936 then s.dt(2, 15, "rng Miels") elseif covt == 1.943844 then s.dt(2, 15, "rng KNots") end s.sc(r, g, b) if speed > 5 then s.dt(2, 21, reachD) else s.dt(2, 21, "--") end end s.sc(40, 40, 40) s.dl(0, 13, 32, 13) s.dl(0, 27, 32, 27) s.drawRect(2, 27, 27, 3) s.sc(r, g, b) s.dF(3, 28, percent*26, 2) s.sc(100, 100, 100, 10) s.sc(100, 250, 100, 70) s.dF(3, 28, percent*26, 1) s.sc(1, 1, 1, 40) s.dl(0, 14, 32, 14) s.dl(0, 0, 32, 0) s.dF(3, 30, percent*26, 1)
s.sc(70, 70, 70, 150) s.dF(((x/600)*24)+3, 28, 2, 2)
end

function isInRect(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end range = 500 count = 30 onoff = false function onTick() if range > 5000 then range = 5000 end if range < 100 then range = 100 end
pressed = input.getBool(1) x = input.getNumber(3) y = input.getNumber(4) output.setNumber(1, range) output.setBool(1, onoff) output.setBool(2, map) onoff = false end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() --Title screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawRect(0,0,w-1,h/4) screen.drawText(2,2,"Range")
--First Button screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) if isInRect(x, y, 0,h/4+1,w/2-1,h/4) and pressed then screen.drawRectF(0,h/4+1,w/2,h/4) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) else screen.drawRect(0,h/4,w/2-1,h/4) end screen.drawText(3,h/4+2,"-") if isInRect(x, y, 0,h/4+1,w/2-1,h/4) and count > 20 and pressed then count = 0 range = range - 100 end
--Second Button screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) if isInRect(x, y, w/2,h/4+1,w/2-1,h/4) and pressed then screen.drawRectF(w/2,h/4+1,w/2,h/4) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) else screen.drawRect(w/2,h/4,w/2-1,h/4) end screen.drawText(w/2+3,h/4+2,"+") if isInRect(x, y, w/2,h/4+1,w/2-1,h/4) and count > 20 and pressed then count = 0 range = range + 100 end
--Third Button screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) if isInRect(x, y, 0,h/2+1,w-1,h/4) and pressed then screen.drawRectF(0,h/2+1,w,h/4) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) else screen.drawRect(0,h/2,w-1,h/4) end screen.drawText(2,h/2+2,"On/Off") if isInRect(x, y, 0,h/2+1,w-1,h/4) and count > 20 and pressed then count = 0 onoff = true end
count=count+1 end

function reset() tick = 0 pointX = {} pointY = {} end
reset() function onTick() tick=tick+1 if tick>480 then reset() end pi = math.pi
value = input.getNumber(1) angle = input.getNumber(31)*pi*2-pi/2 range = input.getNumber(30)
lasttargetdist = targetdist target = input.getBool(1) targetdist = input.getNumber(1) targetangle = input.getNumber(2)*pi*2-pi/2
if target then --When target detected if targetdist <= range then pointX[tick] = (w/2)+math.cos(targetangle)*(targetdist/range)*(w/2) pointY[tick] = (h/2)+math.sin(targetangle)*(targetdist/range)*(h/2) else pointX[tick] = (w/2)+math.cos(targetangle)*(w/2) pointY[tick] = (h/2)+math.sin(targetangle)*(h/2) end end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() pi = math.pi
--Rings screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, w/2) screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 100) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, w/3) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, w/6) --Max Range screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawText(1,h-5,range)
--Dots for i=1,480 do screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawCircleF(pointX[i], pointY[i], 1) end --Rotating Line screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawLine(w/2,h/2,w/2+math.cos(angle)*(w/2),h/2+math.sin(angle)*(h/2)) screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 150) screen.drawTriangleF(w/2,h/2,w/2+math.cos(angle)*(w/2),h/2+math.sin(angle)*(h/2),w/2+math.cos(angle-0.1)*(w/2),h/2+math.sin(angle-0.1)*(h/2)) screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 100) screen.drawTriangleF(w/2,h/2,w/2+math.cos(angle)*(w/2),h/2+math.sin(angle)*(h/2),w/2+math.cos(angle-0.2)*(w/2),h/2+math.sin(angle-0.2)*(h/2)) end

-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 200, 0) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawLine(2, 15, 15, 10) screen.drawLine(28, 15, 15, 10) screen.drawLine(1, h/2, 1, h/2+2) screen.drawLine(w*0.13+1, h/2.2, w*0.13+1, h/2+1) screen.drawLine(w*0.25+1, h/2.5, w*0.25+1, h/2) screen.drawLine(w*0.36+1, h/3, w*0.36+1, h/2-1) screen.drawLine(w*0.77, h/2.2, w*0.77, h/2+1) screen.drawLine(w*0.65, h/2.5, w*0.65, h/2) screen.drawLine(w*0.54, h/3, w*0.54, h/2-1) screen.drawLine(w-3, h/2, w-3, h/2+2) screen.drawLine(w/2-1, h*0.45, w/2-1, h*0.25) screen.drawCircleF(w/2-1,h/3.25,3.2) screen.setColor(50, 255, 50) screen.drawRectF(0, h/2+3, 3, 6) screen.drawRectF(w*0.12, h/2+2, 3, 6) screen.drawRectF(w*0.24, h/2+1, 3, 6) screen.drawRectF(w*0.36, h/2, 3, 7) screen.drawRectF(w*0.91-2, h/2+3, 3, 6) screen.drawRectF(w*0.55-2, h/2, 3, 7) screen.drawRectF(w*0.80-2, h/2+2, 3, 6) screen.drawRectF(w*0.66-2, h/2+1, 3, 6) screen.setColor(255, 100, 0) if isPressed1 then screen.drawRectF(0, h/2+3, 3, 6) end if isPressed2 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.12, h/2+2, 3, 6) end if isPressed3 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.24, h/2+1, 3, 6) end if isPressed4 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.36, h/2, 3, 7) end if isPressed5 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.55-2, h/2, 3, 7) end if isPressed6 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.66-2, h/2+1, 3, 6) end if isPressed7 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.80-2, h/2+2, 3, 6) end if isPressed8 then screen.drawRectF(w*0.91-2, h/2+3, 3, 6) end end

function onTick() w = input.getNumber(1) h = input.getNumber(2) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
ispressing1 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, h/2+3, 3, 6) ispressing2 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.12, h/2+2, 3, 6) ispressing3 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.24, h/2+1, 3, 6) ispressing4 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.36, h/2, 3, 7) ispressing5 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.55-2, h/2, 3, 7) ispressing6 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.66-2, h/2+1, 3, 6) ispressing7 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.80-2, h/2+2, 3, 6) ispressing8 = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w*0.91-2, h/2+3, 3, 6)
output.setBool(1, ispressing1) output.setBool(2, ispressing2) output.setBool(3, ispressing3) output.setBool(4, ispressing4) output.setBool(5, ispressing5) output.setBool(6, ispressing6) output.setBool(7, ispressing7) output.setBool(8, ispressing8) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

Pitch=ipn(3)*(-360) tilt=roll*360 rev=false if Top<0 then tilt=-tilt rev=true end ofS=Pitch l=300 roll=roll*6.28 a1,a2=ipn(4)*(-4),ipn(5)*(-4) end function clamp(n,min,max) if n>max then return max elseif n<min then return min else return n end end function onDraw() --do not edit unless you know what you do, then go nuts with it mx,my=w/2,h/2 sC(0,42,102) uV,rV={sn(rd(tilt)+rd(180)),cs(rd(tilt)+rd(180))},{sn(rd(tilt)+rd(90)),cs(rd(tilt)+rd(90))} if rev then uV,rV={-uV[1],-uV[2]},{-rV[1],-rV[2]} end dtf(mx+(l+ofS)*uV[1]-(l*rV[1])+xo,my+(l+ofS)*uV[2]-(l*rV[2])+yo,mx+l*rV[1]+(ofS)*uV[1]+xo,my+l*rV[2]+(ofS)*uV[2]+yo,mx+(l*rV[1])+((l+ofS)*uV[1])+xo,my+(l*rV[2])+((l+ofS)*uV[2])+yo) sC(0,255,0,210)dL(mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1])+xo,my+((ofS-1)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2])+yo,(mx+((ofS-1)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1])+xo,(my+((ofS-1)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])+yo)dL(mx+((ofS-0.5)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1])+xo,my+((ofS-0.5)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2])+yo,(mx+((ofS-0.5)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1])+xo,(my+((ofS-0.5)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])+yo)dL(mx+((ofS-1.5)*uV[1])-(l*rV[1])+xo,my+((ofS-1.5)*uV[2])-(l*rV[2])+yo,(mx+((ofS-1.5)*uV[1]))+(l*rV[1])+xo,(my+((ofS-1.5)*uV[2]))+(l*rV[2])+yo) for i=10,90,10 do dL(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1])-(5*rV[1])+xo,my+((ofS+i)*uV[2])-(5*rV[2])+yo,(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1]))+(5*rV[1])+xo,(my+((ofS+i)*uV[2]))+(5*rV[2])+yo) end for i=-10,-90,-10 do dL(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1])+(5*rV[1])+xo,my+((ofS+i)*uV[2])+(5*rV[2])+yo,(mx+((ofS+i)*uV[1]))-(5*rV[1])+xo,(my+((ofS+i)*uV[2]))-(5*rV[2])+yo) end sC(10,200,10) x,y=w/2*a1,h/2*a2 screen.drawCircle(w/2+x+xo,h/2+y+yo,4) dL(w/2-4+x+xo,h/2+y+yo,w/2-8+x+xo,h/2+y+yo) dL(w/2+4+x+xo,h/2+y+yo,w/2+8+x+yo,h/2+y+yo)sC(20,255,20)dL(w/2-16+xo,h/2+yo,w/2-8+xo,h/2+yo)dL(w/2+16+xo,h/2+yo,w/2+8+xo,h/2+yo)dL(w/2-8+xo,h/2+yo,w/2-4+xo,h/2+4+yo)dL(w/2-4+xo,h/2+4+yo,w/2+1+xo,h/2-1+yo) dL(w/2+8+xo,h/2+yo,w/2+4+xo,h/2+4+yo) dL(w/2+4+xo,h/2+4+yo,w/2+xo,h/2+yo) sC(160,0,0) end
function dA(...) local x,y,r,a1,a2=... a1=a1 or 0 a2=a2 or 360 step=22.5 if a2<a1 then a2,a1=a1,a2 end local a,px,py,ox,oy,ar = false,0,0,0,0,0 repeat a=a and math.min(a+step,a2) or a1 ar=(a-90)*math.pi/180 px,py=x+r*cs(ar),y+r*sn(ar) if a~=a1 then dL(ox,oy,px,py) end ox,oy = px,py until(a>=a2) end

ipn=input.getNumber sC=screen.setColor sDRf=screen.drawRectF sDR=screen.drawRect dTb=screen.drawTextBox dl=screen.drawLine w,h=64,64 xo,yo=16,16 function onTick() hdg=ipn(8) spdset=ipn(11) altset=ipn(12) spd=ipn(6) if spdset==0 then spd=spd*1.94384 elseif spdset==1 then spd=spd*3.6 elseif spdset==2 then spd=spd*2.23694 end alt=ipn(7) if altset==0 then alt=alt*3.28084 if alt > 7500 then talt=alt/100 else talt=alt end elseif altset==1 then talt=alt end hdg=math.floor(ipn(8)) vs=math.floor(ipn(9)) maxvsspeed=ipn(10) end function onDraw() sC(0,0,0) sDRf(w/2-9+xo,0+yo,19,7) sDRf(-1+xo,h/2-5+yo,21,8) sC(6,6,6,100) sDRf(0+xo,0+yo,21,h) sDRf(w-20+xo,0+yo,20,h) sC(0,255,0)
for i=0,999 do if i<=8 then sC(0,210,0) else sC(0,210,0) end dTb(0+xo,h/2-1-(i*10)+spd+yo,21,6,i*10,0,0) end if altset==0 then
for i=0,99 do if alt > 7500 then dTb(w-20+xo,h/2-1-(i*10)+alt/50+yo,20,6,i*5,0,0) else dTb(w-20+xo,h/2-1-(i*10)+alt/10+yo,20,6,i*100,0,0) end end elseif altset==1 then for i=0,99 do dTb(w-20+xo,h/2-1-(i*10)+alt/10+yo,20,6,i*100,0,0) end end sC(0,0,0) sDRf(0+xo,h-7+yo,17,7) sDRf(w-20+xo,h-7+yo,20,7) sDRf(0+xo,h/2-4+yo,16,7) sDRf(w-20+xo,h/2-4+yo,20,7) if spd<81 then sC(0,210,0) else sC(0,210,0) end
dTb(0+xo,h/2-4+yo,20,7,math.floor(clamp(spd,0,9999)),0,0)
sC(0,210,0) dTb(w-19+xo,h/2-4+yo,20,7,math.floor(clamp(talt,0,9999)),0,0) sDR(w/2-10+xo,-1+yo,19,8) dTb(w/2-8+xo,1+yo,17,6,hdg,0,0) sC(255,0,255) if vs<0 then dl(w-20+xo,32+clamp((math.abs(vs)/maxvsspeed*6)+2,2,16)+yo,w-20+xo,32+yo) else dl(w-20+xo,32-clamp((vs/maxvsspeed*11)+4,5,32)+yo,w-20+xo,32+yo) end sC(0,255,0) sDR(-1+xo,h/2-5+yo,21,8) sDR(w-20+xo,h/2-5+yo,21,8) if spdset==0 then dTb(0+xo,h-7+yo,17,7,"KTS",0,0) elseif spdset==1 then dTb(0+xo,h-7+yo,17,7,"KPH",0,0) elseif spdset==2 then dTb(0+xo,h-7+yo,17,7,"MPH",0,0) elseif spdset==3 then dTb(0+xo,h-7+yo,17,7,"MS",0,0) end if altset==0 then if alt>7500 then dTb(w-20+xo,h-7+yo,20,7,"FL",0,0) else dTb(w-20+xo,h-7+yo,20,7,"FT",0,0) end elseif altset==1 then dTb(w-20+xo,h-7+yo,20,7,"M",0,0) end end function clamp(n,min,max) if n>max then return max elseif n<min then return min else return n end end

offx=64/2 offy=32 xo=16 yo=16 function onTick() roll=math.rad(input.getNumber(1)*360) end function onDraw() for i = 0,100,25 do screen.setColor(10,255,10) angle=math.rad(i-50)+roll x1=12*math.sin(angle)+offx+xo x2=16*math.sin(angle)+offx+xo y1=12*math.cos(angle)+offy+yo y2=16*math.cos(angle)+offy+yo screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end screen.setColor(10,255,10) x1=8*math.sin(0)+offx+xo x2=11*math.sin(0)+offx+xo y1=8*math.cos(0)+offy+yo y2=11*math.cos(0)+offy+yo screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end

Compass=0 HDG=0 w,h=32,32 sC=screen.setColor sDRf=screen.drawRectF sDR=screen.drawRect dTb=screen.drawTextBox dL=screen.drawLine xo=16 yo=17 function onTick() Compass=input.getNumber(1)*-1 HDG=math.floor(((360+Compass)%1)*360) ta=input.getBool(10) end function onDraw() sC(0,0,0) sDRf(0+xo,32+yo,65,32) sC(0,255,0) dL(64/2+xo,94/2-10+yo,64/2+xo,94/2+10+yo) AHand(0,9,5) dL(64/2 -3+xo,94/2+7+yo,64/2 +4+xo,94/2+7+yo) dL(64/2 -10+xo,94/2+yo,64/2 +10+xo,94/2+yo) rMark(math.pi*2*Compass+0.05, 6) rMark(math.pi*2*Compass-0.05, 6) rMark(math.pi*2*Compass, 6) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.75), 5) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.5), 5) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.25), 5) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.25*1/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.25*2/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.25+0.25*1/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.25+0.25*2/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.5+0.25*1/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.5+0.25*2/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.75+0.25*1/3), 2) rMark(math.pi*2*(Compass+0.75+0.25*2/3), 2) sDRf(64/2 -9+xo, 94/2 -4+yo, 18, 9) sC(0, 0, 0, 255) sDRf(64/2 -8+xo, 94/2 -3+yo, 16, 7) sC(0,210,0,255)dTb(64/2-8+xo,94/2-2+yo,16,5,string.format("%03.0f",HDG),0,-1) sC(0,255,0) dL(0+xo,32+yo,64+xo,32+yo) sC(255,255,255) end function rMark(deg, length) screen.drawLine(w/2+16-w/2*math.sin(deg)+xo,h/2+32-h/2*math.cos(deg)+yo,w/2+16-(w/2-length)*math.sin(deg)+xo,h/2+32-(h/2-length)*math.cos(deg)+yo) end function AHand(ALT,length,width) local deg = math.pi*ALT/5 width=width/2 screen.drawTriangleF(64/2+length*math.sin(deg)+xo,94/2-length*math.cos(deg)+yo,64/2-width*math.cos(deg)+xo,94/2-width*math.sin(deg)+yo,64/2+width*math.cos(deg)+xo,94/2+width*math.sin(deg)+yo) end
